reviewText: This was just what I wanted and anticipated. A high quality dvd that is well put together and plays perfectly.
It is a good dvd but not as funny as some of his cds.  Still very enjoyable and will be watched many times.
Another gift for a fan.  The gift pleased the receiver thus pleasing me. It is typical Jerry Clower humor at its best,

This guy is still humorous and clean and may not be everyone's cup of tea but I bet you can find a laugh or two even if you feel you are too sophisticated for Jerry. I really enjoyed the older versions of his humor more though.
I only llistened to this once & enjoyed it.  It was a birthday gift for my son-in-law & he LOVED it!!!  Therefore I am very happy with this product!
First video footage of Jerry that I've ever seen. Grew up listening to his cassette tapes with my father. What a great storyteller. Seeing him perform makes it even better. What a riot!

Jerry Clower was one of the great humorists of the 20th century. Someone once said that a comedian told funny stories, but a humorist
told stories funny. Jerry Clower was one of the best. He could make striking a match funny. Think of him as a country version of
Bill Cosby.
This collection includes two of Clowers live appearances. He`ll have you rolling on the floor with his tales and stories. You will
not be disappointed.

We can use more humoriists like Jerry Clower.  Unlike many people today, Jerry always saw the same world I lived in. And he helped me realize just how lucky I was to be born in the South and to live away from major cities. God bless his soul.
This is classic Jerry Clower.  Good family comedy, where you don't have to worry about language or any inappropriate subjects.
Watching Jerry is not as fun as listening to him.  I didn't find this to be the best of his works by far, though perhaps still a good purchase if you're a die-hard Clower fan.
Gift for my grandfather ...he loved it
Very funny. Wonderful stories that not only make me laugh but also uplifts my spirit.
As always, entertaining.  Old country style humor.  Once you've heard it, that's enough.
Pretty funny got some things on hear that I had not heard before
Great DVD
I ENJOY HIS CLEAN HUMOR AND HIS JOKES NEVER GET OLD THANK YOU.
Great
Scratched but I cleaned & it works ok for an old CD.
As expected!
My dad loves the way he tells a joke with the story line with out any foul language.
Wasn't as funny as I had supposed
very good

This did not include some of the classics that I was looking for. It was as I rated--an ok product. The thought went further than the gift--in this case. For hard core fans or to brighten someone's day by showing them you were thinking about them--this is appropriate.

Jerry Clower is a wonderful, folksy storyteller. He captures the simple dignity of the rural people of the deep South. He also philosophizes about life in general regardless of one's status in society. He has been poor and rich, and he has the wisdom of knowing that riches,while nice if properly earned, are not the main point of life

The best of the best is JERRY CLOWER! I have always loved seeing him on tv
and now I can watch him anytime. Awesome!!!
Jerry Clower is a very funny story teller. Nothing dirty,or degrading. He is just an old country boy telling about what goes on around him. He is great.
Not a lot of content, has a lot of repetative content. A disappointment from what I know could have been put on this DVD.
Good clean humor, it was great.  In today's worl it is hard to find comedy without cursing and sexual content.

We have his CD and it is hilarious and includes a variety of his stories.  I was hoping the DVD contained similar material and was very disappointed.  It centered around one or two stories and wasn't even as long as the CD.  Blah.
Bought this as a gift for my dad. He loves listening to Jerry Clower, so this was a hit with him.
Great storyteller.
Good clean fun loving comedy!!!
Pretty funny

As entertaining as Jerry was, I'm surprised there aren't more video clips available., but there certainly could have been more.  This is certainly a good video to watch, but leaves you wanting more...
It was funny, but not as funny as I remembered from my youth...
Wish we had more like him. Can't say enough.
Great
One of my favorites
Funny but wish it had more of his older ones.
For the son-in-law. He's still laughing!!
